From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Tamer Ahmed <tamerahmed@microsoft.com>
Date: Thu, 18 Jun 2026 00:00:00 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] Pin sdbusplus subproject revision

bmcweb is currently pinned to commit 6926d430, but its sdbusplus Meson
wrap follows HEAD. A newer sdbusplus revision removed the
sdbusplus::message::object_path alias used by this bmcweb revision.

Pin sdbusplus to the last compatible revision before that alias was
removed.
---
 subprojects/sdbusplus.wrap | 12 ++++++------
 1 file changed, 6 insertions(+), 6 deletions(-)

diff --git a/subprojects/sdbusplus.wrap b/subprojects/sdbusplus.wrap
index 7b076d0..a4741c6 100644
--- a/subprojects/sdbusplus.wrap
+++ b/subprojects/sdbusplus.wrap
@@ -1,6 +1,6 @@
-[wrap-git]
-url = https://github.com/openbmc/sdbusplus.git
-revision = HEAD
-
-[provide]
-sdbusplus = sdbusplus_dep
+[wrap-git]
+url = https://github.com/openbmc/sdbusplus.git
+revision = 28722b16b689fc9a0d1d99ceef2db796ee3d162f
+
+[provide]
+sdbusplus = sdbusplus_dep
